name: Bear Market Coin
description: BEAR MARKET COIN is a meme token created to bring a sense of humor and community to one of the most stressful parts of crypto — the market downturn. Instead of pretending bear markets don’t happen, the project leans into them with personality, memes, and a community that enjoys staying united during the red days. It’s about embracing the dip, laughing through the chaos, and giving people a fun identity to rally around.
